      <title>HTB — reversing a custom VM in 3 hours</title>
      <link>https://yourhandle.dev/blog/htb-vm-reversing/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Sep 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://yourhandle.dev/blog/htb-vm-reversing/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The challenge binary implemented a 16-instruction stack VM in ~800 lines&#xA;of C. The flag was encrypted and stored as VM bytecode. My job: reverse&#xA;the ISA, write an emulator in Python, then work backwards from the&#xA;encrypted output to the key.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
